OL,3,CRadioactive gas detected at prison
OL,4,Cleads to closure of 180 cells
OL,6,FA UK prison has had to close down more
OL,7,Fthan 180 cells after radioactive gas
OL,8,Fwas detected, which has also led to
OL,9,Fthe vast majority of nearly 200 recent
OL,10,Fprisoner transfers.
OL,12,FHMP Dartmoor has been forced to close
OL,13,Fthe cells and carry out prisoner
OL,14,Fremovals due to the presence of radon.
OL,16,FThe capacity of the prison has been
OL,17,Freduced by 184 places between November
OL,18,Fand February, with official figures
OL,19,Fsuggesting its total safe capacity is
OL,20,F640.
