OL,6,FIn the same period until February, 194
OL,7,Fprisoners have been moved out of the
OL,8,Fjail.
OL,10,FWhile the reason for their removal is
OL,11,Fnot recorded, it's understood the vast
OL,12,Fmajority have been moved due to radon.
OL,14,FRadon, an odourless and colourless
OL,15,Fgas, is produced by decaying
OL,16,Fradioactive materials in rocks and
OL,17,Fsoils, and is responsible for around
OL,18,F1,000 lung cancer deaths a year.
