OL,6,FIt is thought to occur more often in
OL,7,Fareas with high concentrations of
OL,8,Fgranite, such as Dartmoor.
OL,10,FThe Prison Service said "a number of
OL,11,Fprisoners" had been moved as a
OL,12,Fprecautionary step, with efforts to
OL,13,Freduce radon levels currently ongoing.
OL,15,FThe Labour Party, which revealed the
OL,16,Ffigures in a series of questions to
OL,17,Fministers, said it was "shocking that
OL,18,Fthe Government's mismanagement of the
OL,19,Fprison estate means they are having to
OL,20,Freduce the number of prison places
OL,21,Fduring a capacity crisis".
