OL,6,FRuth Cadbury MP, shadow prisons
OL,7,Fminister, said: "This dangerous gas
OL,8,Fwas first detected in 2020, and yet
OL,9,Fthe Ministry of Justice have said that
OL,10,Fmeasures weren't put in place until
OL,11,F2022.
OL,13,F"Ministers need to explain why it has
OL,14,Ftaken over two years for them to act.
OL,16,F"After 14 years in power and a dozen
OL,17,Fprison ministers, our prisons are out
OL,18,Fof control and the Government need to
OL,19,Fget a grip.
