OL,6,F"Labour will rebuild public confidence
OL,7,Fin the criminal justice system and
OL,8,Fwe'll restore law and order in
OL,9,FBritain."
OL,11,FAnswering Labour's questions on behalf
OL,12,Fof the Government, justice minister
OL,13,FEdward Argar said the Prison Service
OL,14,Fis "continually investing in the
OL,15,Fprison estate to ensure that prisons
OL,16,Fremain safe, decent and secure".
OL,18,FMr Argar said elevated radon readings
OL,19,Fwere detected at Dartmoor in 2020 in
OL,20,F"subterranean areas adjacent to the
OL,21,Fkitchen and workshops".
