OL,6,FHe added: "Temporary mitigations have
OL,7,Fbeen in place at Dartmoor in those
OL,8,Fareas since 2022 following advice from
OL,9,Fspecialist contractors, pending
OL,10,Fpermanent mitigations that are near
OL,11,Fcompletion.
OL,13,F"Further specialist advice has been
OL,14,Fcommissioned following the recent
OL,15,Fidentification of elevated radon
OL,16,Flevels in some accommodation areas of
OL,17,Fthe prison."
