OL,6,FA Prison Service spokesperson said: "A
OL,7,Fnumber of prisoners have been
OL,8,Frelocated as a precautionary measure
OL,9,Fafter routine testing revealed higher
OL,10,Fthan normal levels of radon.
OL,12,F"This is a temporary measure while
OL,13,Fwork to permanently reduce radon
OL,14,Flevels is completed and there are no
OL,15,Fsafety implications to staff or
OL,16,Fprisoners who remain on site."
